<span id="ii.xliv-p17"></span>**8.** Thus did your fathers, when I sent
them from Kadesh-barnea to see the land.

<span id="ii.xliv-p18"></span>**8.** Sic fecerunt patres vestri quando
misi eos de Cades-barnea ut viderent terram istam.

<span id="ii.xliv-p19"></span>**9.** For when they went up unto the
valley of Eshcol, and saw the land, they discouraged the heart of the
