Lord.

<span id="ii.xliv-p46"></span>**22.** Et subjiciatur terra ilia coram
Jehova: postea reveriemini, et eritis absoluti a Jehova, et Israele:
eritque terra ista vobis in possessionem coram Jehova.

<span id="ii.xliv-p47"></span>**23.** But if ye will not do so, behold,
ye have sinned against the Lord: and be sure your sin will find you out.

<span id="ii.xliv-p48"></span>**23.** Quod si non feceritis ita, ecce,
peccastis Jehovae, et perpendite peccatum vestrum quod invenient vos.

<span id="ii.xliv-p49"></span>**24.** Build you cities for your little
