<span id="ii.xliv-p69"></span>**34.** And the children of Gad built
Dibon, and Ataroth, and Aroer,

<span id="ii.xliv-p70"></span>**34.** Et redificaverunt filii Gad Dibon,
et Ataroth, et Aroer,

<span id="ii.xliv-p71"></span>**35.** And Atroth, Shophan, and Jaazer,
and Jogbehah,

<span id="ii.xliv-p72"></span>**35.** Et Atroth, Sopham, et Jaazer, et
Jogbehal,

<span id="ii.xliv-p73"></span>**36.** And Beth-nimrah, and Beth-haran,
fenced cities; and folds for sheep.

<span id="ii.xliv-p74"></span>**36.** Et Beth-nimrah, et Beth-haran,
